00:48:54,207 --> 00:48:55,417
Don't quit, okay?

858
00:48:55,750 --> 00:48:57,169
You can really work for me now

859
00:48:57,169 --> 00:48:58,670
as a true...

860
00:48:59,754 --> 00:49:00,898
personal assistant.

861
00:49:00,922 --> 00:49:03,300
I don't want to work for
you as my boss anymore.

862
00:49:04,323 --> 00:49:06,318
I'd rather pay you to make it up to you.

863
00:49:06,323 --> 00:49:07,574
I just won't be working for you.

864
00:49:07,574 --> 00:49:09,696
No, please.
You don't have to quit, okay?

865
00:49:09,703 --> 00:49:11,345
You can be a real person now.
You can--

866
00:49:11,369 --> 00:49:12,996
You now remove this, right?

867
00:49:13,872 --> 00:49:15,457
- I don't want to!
- Just take it off.

868
00:49:15,957 --> 00:49:17,167
I'm not messing with you.

869
00:49:17,501 --> 00:49:19,645
Just take this off too.
What is that? Is that real?

870
00:49:19,669 --> 00:49:22,209
- Maybe this is also... fake.
- That's a real AI watch!

871
00:49:22,214 --> 00:49:23,752
Let's take it off, shall we?

872
00:49:25,385 --> 00:49:26,468
You might see...

873
00:49:26,471 --> 00:49:28,386
- See, that's better, right?
- ...something else.

874
00:49:28,845 --> 00:49:29,888
Human being...

875
00:49:30,347 --> 00:49:31,806
with emotions.

876
00:49:32,721 --> 00:49:34,848
I was just simply doing my job.

877
00:49:35,602 --> 00:49:36,602
Are you okay, now?

878
00:49:37,312 --> 00:49:38,312
Don't quit.

879
00:49:45,153 --> 00:49:46,153
[chuckling]

880
00:49:46,905 --> 00:49:47,905
Look!

881
00:49:51,451 --> 00:49:52,911
Oh look, here we go.

882
00:50:05,423 --> 00:50:06,423
Hi.

883
00:50:09,469 --> 00:50:10,469
Hi.

884
00:50:12,180 --> 00:50:14,558
We don't need to pretend anymore, Engineer.

885
00:50:15,533 --> 00:50:16,534
We're okay now.

886
00:50:19,676 --> 00:50:21,261
I missed that look on you.

887
00:50:23,692 --> 00:50:25,235
- We even have matching hair.
- AU NATURELLE

888
00:50:28,405 --> 00:50:30,156
So you're copying me, huh?

889
00:50:31,074 --> 00:50:32,367
You inspired me!

890
00:50:37,255 --> 00:50:38,965
I'm gonna miss you, Engineer.

891
00:50:42,836 --> 00:50:44,045
Thank you, Aiko.

892
00:50:46,339 --> 00:50:47,799
Good luck on your first day.

893
00:51:37,307 --> 00:51:38,725
Audio...

894
00:51:41,144 --> 00:51:42,270
Video...

895
00:51:42,562 --> 00:51:43,562
Check!

896
00:52:35,865 --> 00:52:37,176
My outfit doesn't suit me.

897
00:52:37,200 --> 00:52:38,200
No, boss.

898
00:52:38,493 --> 00:52:39,744
It suits you well.

899
00:52:41,253 --> 00:52:42,253
You look handsome.

900
00:52:43,039 --> 00:52:44,039
Ms. Aiko...

901
00:52:44,590 --> 00:52:46,258
You might end up falling in love with Sir.

902
00:52:46,960 --> 00:52:48,979
Oh you really joke a lot, Manang.

903
00:52:49,003 --> 00:52:51,089
No, I'm serious.
You and Sir are perfect for each other.

904
00:52:53,216 --> 00:52:55,343
Oh. Your meeting room is ready.

905
00:52:56,219 --> 00:52:58,638
Cancel the online meeting because today...

906
00:52:59,848 --> 00:53:01,099
We're going to have it in the office.

907
00:53:01,739 --> 00:53:04,784
And this will be your
first day as my legit...

908
00:53:05,353 --> 00:53:06,354
secretary.

909
00:53:07,412 --> 00:53:08,579
Really, boss?

910
00:53:09,023 --> 00:53:12,277
Alright, I'll just text them that the
meeting will be held face-to-face.

911
00:53:14,070 --> 00:53:15,070
Thank you, Manang.

912
00:53:15,488 --> 00:53:17,073
- Take care sir.
- Thank you!

913
00:53:20,910 --> 00:53:21,953
How's the coffee, boss?

914
00:53:23,913 --> 00:53:24,913
It's good.

915
00:53:25,331 --> 00:53:26,916
But it tastes like you made this.

916
00:53:27,959 --> 00:53:29,335
Observation correct.

917
00:53:29,706 --> 00:53:31,040
I taught Manang how to make it.

918
00:53:33,548 --> 00:53:34,674
You're really something.

919
00:53:36,176 --> 00:53:37,176
I love you, Aiko.

920
00:53:37,761 --> 00:53:39,888
You're also something else, boss.
You drink too much coffee.

921
00:53:41,199 --> 00:53:42,199
Let's go?

922
00:53:42,670 --> 00:53:43,670
Let's go.

923
00:53:48,438 --> 00:53:49,439
You smell so good, boss.

924
00:53:49,439 --> 00:53:50,607
Of course I have to keep up!

925
00:53:50,815 --> 00:53:52,312
- Is that so?
- Of course!
